item.title: BHTV
item.description:
BHTV

Stylish 4 Bedroom home on pleasant Parkside Drive in the popular Uplands district near Bradley Park. Features include high ceilings and hardwood floors throughout the main level, a wide foyer with open staircase, 3 well-sized bedrooms on the upper level and an attractively remodeled master suite on the loft level with huge walk-in closet.
